{
  "texts": [
    "Metaphor choice should be considered from a culturally diverse perspective as metaphors may be culturally specific.",
    "Therefore, it is important to choose metaphors that are accessible to target learners.",
    "The 'funhouse mirror' metaphor specifically, may not be familiar to learners from a culture that does not have access to these attractions.",
    "Similarly, the concept of a map can vary across cultures.",
    "This is a limitation of the approach, but it is not insurmountable with careful planning."
  ]
}